 class BinaryFileDataList
          Reads in a binary file, specifically one which has 9 bytes for each rating, broken up into: 4 bytes for the user number 4 bytes for the item number 1 byte for the item rating (multiplied by a factor of 2) This has been specifically coded for the movieLens data, though other data transformed ot this format will also work.
